00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:40,910
[Story of Nangong]

2
00:00:42,020 --> 00:00:43,700
I still have to

3
00:00:45,100 --> 00:00:46,340
show

4
00:00:47,790 --> 00:00:49,990
His Majesty some respect.

5
00:00:57,820 --> 00:00:58,550
Get out!

6
00:00:58,860 --> 00:01:01,100
Don't ever appear before me again,

7
00:01:01,120 --> 00:01:03,070
or I will definitely kill you.

8
